HAVEN / 33 Acres Brewing Co. ‘Super Crisp’ Rice Lager

Inspired by countless journeys and shared experiences, this crisp, refreshing lager is a celebration of friendships and connections made over cold drinks and good food.

Crafted with balance and precision, it offers a smooth, clean finish, perfect for those moments when conversation flows and relationships are forged. Brewed to a crisp index of 3000, this lager embodies the spirit of togetherness behind every sip.

Enjoyed best with friends, family or solo.

Join us this Thursday, November 14th from 5-10pm at 33 Acres Brewing in Vancouver for an exclusive launch event. Learn more via the link in bio.
